132
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,480
maaaring sundin ang kanilang puso

133
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,730
at gawin ang anumang nais nilang gawin.

134
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,600
Sabay tayong lumaki

135
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:07,670
at mas naiintindihan ang bawat isa.

136
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:09,750
May mga dahilan ako.

137
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:12,960
Bago ako bumalik,

138
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,320
