ang malalim na ugat ng mga sakit ng Great Yong.

206
00:14:19,630 --> 00:14:21,960
Saka lamang matatamasa ni Ximeng ang pangmatagalang kapayapaan.

207
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:23,360
Sa aking pagbabalik,

208
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:25,230
Tutuparin ko ang pangako ko

209
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,590
at muling makakasama mo.

210
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,500
Chu, gising ka na pala.

211
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,670
At nawala na ang lagnat mo.

212
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:54,930
Dapat okay ka na ngayon.

213
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,030
Lady Chu, mangyaring huminahon.

214
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,080
Ilang araw ka nang walang malay.

215
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:01,270
Napakahina ng iyong katawan.

216
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:02,800
Hihilingin ko kay Minglu na tulungan ka.

217
00:15:08,550 --> 00:15:09,480
Nasaan si Minglu?

218
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:16,440
Ano nga ba ang nangyari?

219
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,600
Bago umalis si Minglu,

220
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:30,160
